messageBody:
Hi Spider,

Please check whether the attached document is useful to you.
I have prepared it for my reference.

You can search in google for JUnit Cookbook, or JUnit Tutorial to get
some comprehensive tutorials.

Have a nice time.

-----Original Message-----
From: spiderman8083 [mailto:spiderman8083@...]
Sent: Thursday, March 18, 2004 1:49 AM
To: junit@yahoogroups.com
Subject: [junit] junit learning guide


Please tell me the best books/online tutorials(preferably free) for
learning junit in the most basic, easiest way possible. I need to know
for school.

I searched amazon and came up with "Junit in action" (which may have
been a bit advanced) and Java Tools for Extreme Programming, which
seemed more basic but did have some negative reviews (but 4 stars
overall).
